text: Wacław Orłowski (born 5 January 1945) is a Polish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 97 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1945 births Category:Living people Category:Polish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Poland Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Braunau am Inn
